","funnels":"Funnels & Conversion Rate Optimization","branding":"Branding","contentMarketing":"Content Marketing","emailMarketing":"Email Marketing & Automation","socialMedia":"Social Media Management","videoMarketing":"Video Marketing","analytics":"Analytics & Reporting","cro":"Conversion Rate Optimization","growthConsulting":"Growth Strategy & Consulting","content":"Content","webDesignShort":"Web Design","funnelsShort":"Funnels & CRO"},"footer":{"tagline":"We turn inconsistent traffic into predictable revenue systems.","navigation":"Navigation","services":"Services","contact":"Contact","copyright":"KINEXIS Digital. All rights reserved.","builtWith":"Built with strategy, not templates.","missionTitle":"We take on 8–10 clients at a time.","missionBody":"Focused engagements. Real results. No cookie-cutter playbooks.","privacy":"Privacy Policy","terms":"Terms of Service","locations":"Locations"},"common":{"bookStrategyCall":"Book a Strategy Call","scheduleStrategyCall":"Schedule a Strategy Call","learnAboutUs":"Learn About Us","viewAllServices":"View All Services","viewOurWork":"View Our Work","viewCaseStudy":"View Case Study","viewAllCaseStudies":"View All Case Studies","outcomeComparison":"Outcome comparison","getFreeAudit":"Get Free Audit","requestProposal":"Request Proposal","atAGlance":"At a Glance"},"language":{"label":"Language","en":"English","es":"Español (LATAM)"},"hero":{"line1":"WE DON'T","line2":"GENERATE LEADS.","line3":"WE BUILD","line3Highlight":"MARKET DOMINANCE.","subtitle":"The infrastructure that moves qualified traffic toward revenue: technical, creative, and strategic, built as one coordinated program.|Not a list of services. A system."},"revenueEngine":{"label":"The KINEXIS Framework","title":"Visibility → Traffic → Leads → Revenue","subtitle":"Four stages. Each one depends on the last. Skip one and the whole thing leaks.","liveTrajectory":"Live trajectory","stage":"Stage","trajectoryPeriod":"7-month trajectory","metricStart":"Start","metricCurrent":"Current","chartStart":"Start","chartEnd":"Now","stages":{"visibility":{"label":"Visibility","description":"Qualified visitors from search, social, and paid channels","tags":["SEO","Paid Ads","Social"]},"traffic":{"label":"Traffic","description":"Pages built to convert, wherever people find you","tags":["Landing Pages","Lead Magnets"]},"leads":{"label":"Leads","description":"Frictionless capture and strategic sales conversations","tags":["Forms","Discovery Calls"]},"revenue":{"label":"Revenue","description":"Predictable growth in recurring revenue and lifetime value","tags":["MRR","LTV"]}},"chartUnits":{"visibility":"impressions (K)","traffic":"sessions (K)","leads":"leads/mo","revenue":"$$K MRR"}},"servicesEcosystem":{"label":"Connected Services","title":"Services that work together.","subtitle":"SEO feeds content. Content feeds funnels. Funnels feed email. Run them separately and they perform like separate services. Build them as one program and each one amplifies the rest."},"featuredResults":{"label":"Proven Results","title":"Outcomes, not opinions.","subtitle":"Three verified client results across home services and technology. Strategy, execution timeline, and real revenue numbers.","cases":{"landscaping":{"category":"Home Services","title":"Landscaping Company","headline":"4.8X Qualified Lead Growth","summary":"A complete SEO and site rebuild. Qualified leads went from 10 to 48 per month, organic traffic up 1,290%, and conversion rate from 1.8% to 8.4%."},"plumbing":{"category":"Home Services","title":"Plumbing Company","headline":"327% More Emergency Calls","summary":"Family-owned plumber escaped paid ad dependency. Emergency calls went from 22 to 94 per month, ad spend cut by 65%, and local pack dominance achieved."},"saas":{"category":"Technology","title":"SaaS Platform","headline":"5.9X More Demos","summary":"B2B SaaS scaled demo requests from 32 to 189 per month through content marketing and technical SEO. MRR grew from $8.5K to $33K in 8 months."}}},"philosophy":{"label":"Why Clients Switch To KINEXIS","title":"You've been here before.","subtitle":"Another agency. Another promise. Another quarterly report full of impressions that don't touch your pipeline.","before":"Before","after":"After","agencyA":"Agency A","beforeItems":["Slow communication","No reporting","No transparency","Vanity metrics","Rotating account managers"],"afterItems":["Weekly reporting","Clear KPIs","Dedicated strategist","Revenue-focused metrics","Direct access to leadership"],"statusBefore":"Disconnected","statusAfter":"Revenue-aligned","dashboardBefore":"Q4 dashboard","dashboardAfter":"Live KPI board","pipelineLabel":"Pipeline value","pipelineBefore":"↓ 22%","pipelineAfter":"↑ 3.2×","statImpressions":"Impressions","statEngagement":"Engagement","statRevenue":"Revenue","beforeItemDetails":["Three-day email loops and vague updates. Urgent issues wait until your next scheduled call while ad spend keeps burning.","A PDF once a quarter, if you're lucky. No visibility into what's working, what's wasted, or what changed last week.","Black-box billing and unclear scope. You never know who's doing the work or where your budget actually goes.","They celebrate impressions and clicks while your pipeline stays flat. Activity looks busy. Revenue does not move.","Every quarter someone new owns your account. Context resets and you're re-explaining your business from scratch."],"afterItemDetails":["Every Monday: spend, leads, CPL, and pipeline in one digest. You always know where you stand and what's being optimized.","We agree on targets upfront: revenue, cost per lead, conversion rate. We report against them every week.","One senior strategist owns your account end-to-end. They know your business, market, and numbers. No handoffs.","We track what hits your P&L: qualified leads, close rate, ROAS, and LTV. Vanity metrics are context, never the headline.","Skip the ticket queue. When something matters, you're talking to decision-makers who can change direction fast."]},"cta":{"label":"Let's Talk","title":"Ready to Build a","titleHighlight":"Revenue System?","subtitle":"No deck. No rehearsed presentation. Bring your actual situation: what's not working, what you've already tried, what you're hoping to fix. We'll have an honest conversation about whether we can help."},"midCta":{"label":"Next Step","title":"See what's possible|for your business","subtitle":"Book a call. We'll show you exactly where your marketing is leaking and what a real fix would cost.","secondaryCta":"Get Free Audit"},"chatbot":{"openChat":"Open chat","closeChat":"Close chat","chatMessage":"Chat message","sendMessage":"Send message","assistantName":"KINEXIS AI","assistantRole":"Sales assistant","placeholder":"Type your answer...","initialMessage":"Quick question: are you looking for SEO, paid ads, web design, or something else?","questions":{"service":"What service are you looking for? (SEO, Paid Ads, Web Design, Funnels, Branding)","business":"What type of business do you run?","revenue":"What's your monthly revenue range?","goal":"What's your primary goal? (leads, sales, brand growth)"},"quickReplies":{"services":["SEO","Paid Ads","Web Design","Funnels","Branding"],"businessTypes":["E-Commerce","Local Service","SaaS","Professional Services"],"revenue":["Under $10k/mo","$$10k-$50k/mo","$$50k-$100k/mo","$$100k+/mo"],"goals":["More leads","More sales","Brand awareness","All of the above"]},"highIntentResponse":"You sound like a great fit! Let's get you booked for a strategy call. 👇","lowIntentResponse":"Thanks! Start with our free growth audit. It'll give you a clear picture of where to focus. 👇"},"cookies":{"title":"We use cookies","description":"We use essential cookies to run this site and, with your consent, analytics cookies to understand how visitors use kinexisdigital.com. See our","privacyLink":"Privacy Policy","accept":"Accept analytics","reject":"Reject non-essential"},"notFound":{"title":"Page not found","body":"The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved. Here are a few places to continue.","home":"Homepage","services":"Services","contact":"Contact","cta":"Book a strategy call","footnote":"No long-term contracts. Month to month."}},"now":"$undefined","timeZone":"America/Bogota","children":"$L1e"}]
